full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/18/2023 U. S. DEPARTMENT OF LABOR IMMIGRATION SERVICE DISTRICT No. 31 IN ANSWERING REFER TO No. 9402/157 DEPARTMENT JUL 31 aceives OFFICE OF DISTRICT DIRECTOR LOS ANGELES, CALIF. July 29, 1933. Inspector in Charge, U. S. Immigration Service, Los Angeles, Calif. Local 1933 OFFICE Subject: WONG GUCK ( KWOCK) ON, Applicant for citizen's return certificate, Form 430, your # 8402/196. Triplicate of form 430 inthe case of the above applicant, duly approved, is inclosed herewith. The original of form 430; C. I. # 67098; S. P. file # 7402/99; transcript of testimony and report are being forwarded to the San Pedro office. The applicant should be instructed to call there and exchange the duplicate of 430 for the original thereof before his departure for China. / family Harry B. Blee Asst. District Director of Immigration Los Angeles District. R July 31,1933 Mailed Duplicate of the Form to Applicant. JCN Jen
